                                        <p>
                                            Undergo a screening test to ensure your eligibility for donation. This step helps maintain the health and safety of both the donor and the recipient.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="arrow"></div>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <!-- Left Box -->
                        <article class="process_donate_item">
                            <div class="card_box">
